import * as React from "react"
import Toolbar from "@mui/material/Toolbar"
import Typography from "@mui/material/Typography"
import styled from "styled-components"
import AOS from "aos"
import { useEffect } from "react"
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  FormControl,
  Grid2,
  InputAdornment,
  InputLabel,
  Link,
  OutlinedInput,
} from "@mui/material"
import Input from "../../component/Input"
import SearchIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Search"
import { BorderAll, Opacity } from "@mui/icons-material"

// Styling the Navbar text
const NavbarText = styled(Typography)`
  color: white;
  font-family: "poppins";
`
const TopBar = styled(Box)`
  background-color: black;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  height: 44px;
  /* display: none; */
`

const NavbarMaintext = styled(Navbar)`
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
`
const Navbartext = styled(Typography)`
  font-family: "Poppins";
`

const Bartext = styled(Grid2)`
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
  align-items: center;
`

const Searchbar = styled(Grid2)`
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  /* margin-left: 5px; */
`
const NavbarMain = styled(Box)`
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin-top: 12px;`



const Searchicon=styled(SearchIcon)`

  
`

export default function Navbar() {
  useEffect(() => {
    AOS.init({
      duration: 2000,
    })
  }, [])

  return (
    <>
      <TopBar>
        <Toolbar>
          <NavbarText>
            Summer Sale: All Swim Suits And Free Express Delivery - OFF 50%!
            Shop Now
          </NavbarText>
        </Toolbar>
      </TopBar>





      <NavbarMain>
        <Container>
          <Grid2 container alignItems={"center"} justifyContent={"center"} spacing={4}>
            <Grid2 size={2}>
              <Typography variant="h4"> Exclisive </Typography>
            </Grid2>

            <Bartext size={6}>
              <Box>
                <Navbartext></Navbartext>
                <Link href="#" underline="hover">
                  Home
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box>
                <Link href="#" underline="hover">
                  Contact
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box>
                <Link href="#" underline="hover">
                  About
                </Link>
              </Box>
              <Box>
                <Link href="#" underline="hover">
                  Sign Up
                </Link>
              </Box>
            </Bartext>

            <Searchbar size={4}>
              <Box>
               <Input type="text" label="what are you looking for ?" name="usearch"  variant="outlined" style={{BorderAll:0,Opacity:"50%"}}/> 
               <Searchicon/>
              </Box>
            </Searchbar>
          </Grid2>
        </Container>
      </NavbarMain>
    </>
  )
}
